Embedding  & Vector search

- Embedding is a way to convert the text into list of numbers (use Embedding Models), so that this can be easily stored in a vector Store - helpfull in similarity search (semantic search)
- ex: generating the similar color to green, this would not be stored anywhere , it uses vector search to identify the similar likeihood colors
